Data Preparation:

Prepare a CSV file with Name and Email columns

Optional: add other columns for reference

Email Configuration:

Set the message subject

Create the HTML template for email body

Use variables for personalization

Attachments (Optional):

Associate specific files with each contact

Or send the same attachment to multiple people

Sending:

Click "Start Sending"

System applies automatic delays between sends

Real-time monitoring in execution log

üé® Graphical Interface
Main Screen
Section 1: Database loading and editing

Section 2: Email configuration (subject, body, attachments)

Section 3: Sending controls (start, stop, clear)

Section 4: Real-time execution log

Progress Bar: Visual sending tracking

Auxiliary Windows
Data Editor: Editable table to modify contacts

Attachment Manager: Interface to associate files

Data Viewer: Read-only table for visualization

